  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Main objective: investigate whether a functional polymorphism of CR1 (length, number of
      binding sites in C4b C3b, erythrocyte density, rate of soluble CR1 ...) so determined genetic
      or acquired, is a susceptibility factor for the disease Alzheimer's.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
